            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 200px;">
                    <p>含有 <span class="keyword">n 个结点</span> 和 <span class="keyword">m 条边</span> 的图。</p>
                    <ul style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem;">
                        <li><strong>n (Order):</strong> 阶数，顶点数 |V|</li>
                        <li><strong>m (Size):</strong> 边数 |E|</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="diagram-container" style="flex: 1; border: none; background: transparent; height: auto;">
